---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Section from '../../components/sections/Section.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Financial Disclaimer | IBC Academy"
  description="Important financial disclaimer for IBC Academy. Educational content only — not financial, tax, or legal advice."
>
  <Section>
    <div class="prose-wrapper">
      <h1 class="prose-title">Financial Disclaimer</h1>
      <p class="prose-updated">Last updated: January 27, 2025</p>

      <h2 class="prose-heading">About Brad Raschke & IBC Academy</h2>
      <p class="prose-text">
        Brad Raschke is a licensed insurance professional and an Authorized Infinite Banking
        Concept (IBC) Practitioner through the Nelson Nash Institute. IBC Academy
        (ibcacademy.org) is an educational platform created by Brad to help individuals
        understand the Infinite Banking Concept as taught by R. Nelson Nash.
      </p>

      <h2 class="prose-heading">Educational Purposes Only</h2>
      <p class="prose-text">
        All content provided on this website — including articles, lessons, videos, tools,
        and downloadable resources — is for educational and informational purposes only.
        Nothing on this site constitutes financial advice, investment advice, tax advice,
        legal advice, or any other form of professional advice. The information presented
        is intended to help you understand the Infinite Banking Concept; it is not a
        recommendation to purchase any specific financial product.
      </p>

      <h2 class="prose-heading">Not Financial Advice</h2>
      <p class="prose-text">
        The content on IBC Academy should not be interpreted as personalized financial
        advice or a recommendation to buy, sell, or hold any insurance product, security,
        or financial instrument. Every individual's financial situation is unique, and the
        strategies discussed on this site may not be appropriate for everyone.
      </p>
      <p class="prose-text">
        Before making any financial decisions — including purchasing whole life insurance
        or implementing any strategy discussed on this site — you should consult with
        qualified professionals, including a licensed insurance agent, financial advisor,
        tax professional, and/or attorney who can evaluate your specific circumstances.
      </p>

      <h2 class="prose-heading">No Specific Products</h2>
      <p class="prose-text">
        IBC Academy does not sell, recommend, or endorse any specific insurance products,
        financial products, or investment vehicles on this website. No specific insurance
        policies, carriers, or product illustrations are discussed, offered, or promoted
        on ibcacademy.org. Any discussion of insurance products on this site is purely
        educational and generic in nature.
      </p>
      <p class="prose-text">
        For individuals who are interested in exploring specific insurance products or IBC
        implementation, Brad Raschke operates separately through
        <a href="https://1322legacystrategies.com" class="prose-link" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">1322 Legacy Strategies</a>,
        where he works with qualified prospects in a licensed professional capacity.
      </p>

      <h2 class="prose-heading">No Guarantees of Results</h2>
      <p class="prose-text">
        IBC Academy makes no guarantees regarding the outcomes of applying the concepts
        discussed on this site. Individual results will vary based on personal financial
        circumstances, policy design, insurance carrier performance, economic conditions,
        and many other factors. Past performance of any financial product or strategy does
        not guarantee future results.
      </p>
      <p class="prose-text">
        Any examples, case studies, or hypothetical illustrations presented on this site
        are for educational purposes only and do not represent guarantees or projections
        of future performance.
      </p>

      <h2 class="prose-heading">Third-Party Content</h2>
      <p class="prose-text">
        This website may contain links to third-party websites, resources, or content.
        These links are provided for convenience and educational purposes only. IBC Academy
        does not endorse, control, or assume responsibility for the content, accuracy, or
        practices of any third-party websites.
      </p>

      <h2 class="prose-heading">Professional Credentials</h2>
      <p class="prose-text">
        Brad Raschke's credentials include being a licensed insurance professional and an
        Authorized IBC Practitioner as recognized by the Nelson Nash Institute. These
        credentials relate to his professional practice and do not imply that the
        educational content on this website constitutes professional advice.
      </p>

      <h2 class="prose-heading">Contact</h2>
      <p class="prose-text">
        If you have questions about this disclaimer or the educational content on IBC
        Academy, please reach out through the contact information provided on this website.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .prose-wrapper {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .prose-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--color-navy, #1B2A4A);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .prose-title {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }
  }

  .prose-updated {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #5A6B8A);
    margin: 0 0 2.5rem 0;
  }

  .prose-heading {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: var(--color-navy, #1B2A4A);
    margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .prose-text {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #5A6B8A);
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .prose-text:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .prose-link {
    color: var(--color-gold, #C8962E);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .prose-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-navy, #1B2A4A);
  }
</style>
